How did she manage to escape again?

29
00:03:13,730 --> 00:03:16,370
[Maple Inn]

30
00:03:26,280 --> 00:03:27,430
Brother Xie,

31
00:03:27,579 --> 00:03:28,210
are you alright?

32
00:03:29,710 --> 00:03:30,520
Miss Yunyun.

33
00:03:31,670 --> 00:03:32,590
Why are you here?

34
00:03:32,590 --> 00:03:34,660
